{"tid":1126853,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Nature重磅：華裔科學家成功解碼腦電波，AI直接從大腦中合成語音","createTime":"2019-04-26T16:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T10:27:46.000Z","uid":80481,"like":114,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"e7be9a4cc8ac01edcd94ecdaf2008d59d18bed22","tid":1126853,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:06:45.000Z","msg":"大腦活動能夠解碼成語音了。<br />\n<br />\n  說話似乎是一項毫不費力的活動，但它其實是人類最複雜的動作之一。說話需要精確、動態地協調聲道發音器官結構中的肌肉&mdash;&mdash;嘴唇、舌頭、喉部和下頜。當由於中風、肌萎縮側索硬化症或其他神經系統疾病而導致言語中斷時，喪失說話能力可能是毀滅性的。<br />\n<br />\n  來自加州大學舊金山分校的科學家創造了更接近能夠恢復說話功能的腦機接口（brain&ndash;computer interface， BCI）。<br />\n<br />\n腦機接口旨在幫助癱瘓患者直接從大腦中&ldquo;讀取&rdquo;他們的意圖，並利用這些信息控制外部設備或移動癱瘓的肢體，這項技術目前能夠使癱瘓的人每分鐘最多能打出8個單詞，而加州大學舊金山分享的研究人員開發了一種方法，使用深度學習方法直接從大腦信號中產生口語句子，達到150個單詞，接近正常人水平！<br />\n<br />\n  這項研究發表在最新一期《自然》雜誌上，作者為Anumanchipalli以及華裔科學家Edward Chang等人。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/crawl/10/w550h260/20190425/hNLs-hvvuiyn9685486.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftech%2Fcrawl%2F10%2Fw550h260%2F20190425%2FhNLs-hvvuiyn9685486.jpg&h=c40f8ec8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每分鐘能夠生成150單詞，接近正常人類水平<br />\n<br />\n  加州大學舊金山分校的研究人員與5名志願者合作，志願者們接受了一項被稱為&ldquo;顱內監測&rdquo;的實驗，其中電極被用於監測大腦活動，作為癲癇治療的一部分。<br />\n<br />\n  許多癲癇患者的藥物治療效果並不好，他們選擇接受腦部手術。在術前，醫生必須首先找到病人大腦中癲癇發作的&ldquo;熱點&rdquo;，這一過程是通過放置在大腦內部或表面的電極來完成的，並監測明顯的電信號高峰。<br />\n<br />\n  精確定位&ldquo;熱點&rdquo;的位置可能需要數週時間。在此期間，患者通過植入大腦區域或其附近的電極來度日，這些區域涉及運動和聽覺信號。這些患者一般會同意利用這些植入物進行額外的實驗。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/crawl/162/w550h412/20190425/drSY-hvvuiyn9685511.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftech%2Fcrawl%2F162%2Fw550h412%2F20190425%2FdrSY-hvvuiyn9685511.jpg&h=102c024e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此次招募的五名志願者同意測試虛擬語音發生器。每個患者都植入了一兩個電極陣列：圖章大小的、包含幾百個微電極的小墊，放置在大腦表面。<br />\n<br />\n  實驗要求參與者背誦幾百個句子，電極會記錄運動皮層中神經元的放電模式。研究人員將這些模式與患者在自然說話時嘴唇，舌頭，喉部和下頜的微小運動聯繫起來。然後將這些動作翻譯成口語化的句子。<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/tech/crawl/335/w550h585/20190425/4ish-hvvuiyn9685529.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftech%2Fcrawl%2F335%2Fw550h585%2F20190425%2F4ish-hvvuiyn9685529.jpg&h=3bdfdd27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n實驗要求母語為英語的人聽這些句子，以測試虛擬語音的流暢性。研究發現，大約70%的虛擬系統生成的內容是可理解的。<br />\n<br />\n  最終，這套新系統每分鐘能夠生成150單詞，接近自然講話的語速水平。而以前基於植入物的通信系統每分鐘可以生成大約8個單詞。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-019-01181-y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fd41586-019-01181-y&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjpKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=4b97169a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-019-01181-y</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://tech.sina.com.cn/csj/2019-04-25/doc-ihvhiqax4970790.shtml\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftech.sina.com.cn%2Fcsj%2F2019-04-25%2Fdoc-ihvhiqax4970790.shtml&d=tLsEO8KpRnvfRHW%2FlT3TjpKhd8YmQljH21R%2F5cbT5WU%3D&h=be16d911\" target=\"_blank\">http://tech.sina.com.cn/csj/2019-04-25/doc-ihvhiqax4970790.shtml</a>"},{"pid":"325f6f3da331baff4ed8533109c1d6f9b2d2a280","tid":1126853,"uid":222475,"like":169,"dislike":2,"score":167,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"諗到乜就直接講，佢哋咪講唔到大話？"},{"pid":"8c2b3d69b320959677b27c2c935c795d14c6a8a6","tid":1126853,"uid":66811,"like":29,"dislike":3,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:11:26.000Z","msg":"可以同植物人溝通?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c91e407d852311ec8ed9dcd31a40bc5ecc2dfb","tid":1126853,"uid":31098,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"Edward Chang<br />\n咁應該係台灣人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0ac3ca03400c7538b7dd1d8ca7b97a9ac09a761","tid":1126853,"uid":17496,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:13:41.000Z","msg":"華人研究<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7288420fa2a98ddc5970cc97d718b5c7d0a3606d","tid":1126853,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:15:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9bf7c71a144426da041b035e0717cd076432a5","tid":1126853,"uid":63846,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:20:22.000Z","msg":"都唔係first author<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bf788f0717040d0980e99c61b04668df9536a1","tid":1126853,"uid":69013,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"be9bf7c71a144426da041b035e0717cd076432a5","tid":1126853,"uid":63846,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:20:22.000Z","msg":"都唔係first author<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:24:18.000Z","msg":"通訊作者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d05112540bf0bcf505c872f4e49d27f0f74eb19","tid":1126853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17c91e407d852311ec8ed9dcd31a40bc5ecc2dfb","tid":1126853,"uid":31098,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"Edward Chang<br />\n咁應該係台灣人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:26:47.000Z","msg":"點解？"},{"pid":"783215d9594696de63c2a3ab728ad550e04020d6","tid":1126853,"uid":188421,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"17c91e407d852311ec8ed9dcd31a40bc5ecc2dfb","tid":1126853,"uid":31098,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"Edward Chang<br />\n咁應該係台灣人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"北美好多Asian 姓Chang，唔一定台灣"},{"pid":"b1c83f3e331ab3d8e3a3003cac4b3107a1c00aa7","tid":1126853,"uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"783215d9594696de63c2a3ab728ad550e04020d6","tid":1126853,"uid":188421,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"17c91e407d852311ec8ed9dcd31a40bc5ecc2dfb","tid":1126853,"uid":31098,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:11:55.000Z","msg":"Edward Chang<br />\n咁應該係台灣人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:12:15.000Z","msg":"北美好多Asian 姓Chang，唔一定台灣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:13:30.000Z","msg":"可能係香港人"},{"pid":"ffc044f3b26f693ad6bcc61d5521ec140c61a67a","tid":1126853,"uid":48796,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:20:59.000Z","msg":"「呢條女個波好大，仆街，說了出來」"},{"pid":"8f21ff2d6d8fcb6ac9e75a88f37b28c09f15c968","tid":1126853,"uid":204929,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ffc044f3b26f693ad6bcc61d5521ec140c61a67a","tid":1126853,"uid":48796,"like":88,"dislike":0,"score":88,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:20:59.000Z","msg":"「呢條女個波好大，仆街，說了出來」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:23:41.000Z","msg":"會唔會被metoo?"},{"pid":"af6b26b816c7a54fcd0d6e990a86f8c1c6f8b93d","tid":1126853,"uid":24730,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"畀支共偷到技術就大撚鑊鳥"},{"pid":"691018649bef1e6085e85885d155c5e32bbe1bfc","tid":1126853,"uid":170229,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"325f6f3da331baff4ed8533109c1d6f9b2d2a280","tid":1126853,"uid":222475,"like":169,"dislike":2,"score":167,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"諗到乜就直接講，佢哋咪講唔到大話？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:26:01.000Z","msg":"實驗要求參與者背誦幾百個句子，電極會記錄運動皮層中神經元的放電模式。研究人員將這些模式與患者在自然說話時嘴唇，舌頭，喉部和下頜的微小運動聯繫起來。然後將這些動作翻譯成口語化的句子。<br />\n<br />\n你要講嘢，首先要組織句子，然後要計劃如何用肌肉去講，最後先係講。所有行動都有個planning phase 同 execution phase.之所以平時你唔覺係因為你大腦已經好習慣做啲平常嘢，所以會好快完咗planning phase(就好似copy and paste 個 template 咁樣），直接execute.<br />\n<br />\n(同時悲觀/長期抑鬱嘅人都會因為sad 得太耐，變咗做習慣，喺判斷事情嘅時候都會form 咗個template, aka neural pathway, 而更難脫離個種心態）<br />\n<br />\n而如果你睇返上文，佢係要埋啲patient execute (自然說話）先翻譯。所以唔會一諗到嘢（組織=planning phase) 就講。<br />\n<br />\n利伸好耐之前對neuroscience 好有興趣，不過都係求其睇咗小小，唔一定啱。"},{"pid":"4a9bf04360b0365ace5411f6c88add21d16f0a4c","tid":1126853,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af6b26b816c7a54fcd0d6e990a86f8c1c6f8b93d","tid":1126853,"uid":24730,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:24:46.000Z","msg":"畀支共偷到技術就大撚鑊鳥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:26:10.000Z","msg":"如果個科學家係中國人就唔洗偷啦"},{"pid":"6e00e8fbcaf701953d97b3c0ad65e71856dc5bc1","tid":1126853,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:33:40.000Z","msg":"誠實豆沙包"},{"pid":"00ae080355992bf3a8e4590d7a16d3d30cbb183c","tid":1126853,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:34:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97878d8195ee6247dc445ee796f976e2faeaa010","tid":1126853,"uid":41245,"like":64,"dislike":10,"score":54,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:40:20.000Z","msg":"支那人真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n份paper係三個authors<br />\n個「華裔」就排最尾嘅<br />\n噉都要拎嚟做標題打飛機"},{"pid":"3b8c9d72d0f0c76852c7b04891e27c5cd7c5e561","tid":1126853,"uid":167658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:46:37.000Z","msg":"覺得條女好正咪會直接講？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2fa4ec5c03a5118a24cb5619066927141ce4fbb","tid":1126853,"uid":27885,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:47:07.000Z","msg":"And a vision that was planted in my brain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPeople talking w