dBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:28:04.000Z","msg":"反方向就係inception仲恐怖"},{"pid":"4f805d348ab5108c6559644dd5161c7ec46360ef","tid":1126853,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"691018649bef1e6085e85885d155c5e32bbe1bfc","tid":1126853,"uid":170229,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"quote":{"pid":"325f6f3da331baff4ed8533109c1d6f9b2d2a280","tid":1126853,"uid":222475,"like":169,"dislike":2,"score":167,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"諗到乜就直接講，佢哋咪講唔到大話？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T18:26:01.000Z","msg":"實驗要求參與者背誦幾百個句子，電極會記錄運動皮層中神經元的放電模式。研究人員將這些模式與患者在自然說話時嘴唇，舌頭，喉部和下頜的微小運動聯繫起來。然後將這些動作翻譯成口語化的句子。<br />\n<br />\n你要講嘢，首先要組織句子，然後要計劃如何用肌肉去講，最後先係講。所有行動都有個planning phase 同 execution phase.之所以平時你唔覺係因為你大腦已經好習慣做啲平常嘢，所以會好快完咗planning phase(就好似copy and paste 個 template 咁樣），直接execute.<br />\n<br />\n(同時悲觀/長期抑鬱嘅人都會因為sad 得太耐，變咗做習慣，喺判斷事情嘅時候都會form 咗個template, aka neural pathway, 而更難脫離個種心態）<br />\n<br />\n而如果你睇返上文，佢係要埋啲patient execute (自然說話）先翻譯。所以唔會一諗到嘢（組織=planning phase) 就講。<br />\n<br />\n利伸好耐之前對neuroscience 好有興趣，不過都係求其睇咗小小，唔一定啱。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:34:09.000Z","msg":"又學到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3609fc9116fad7129ac5bca050fc13e1860d86b6","tid":1126853,"uid":145277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-27T03:35:48.000Z","msg":"遲d會唔會呈交比習習做思想監控<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959f7a2130db93055b57afbeaee1c50b561e360e","tid":1126853,"uid":145277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pi